Haunting
Discworld ritual help
Haunting

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Haunting - Makes a target become edgy and suspicious.
.EP

.SH Description
This is an offensive, illusory ritual, that makes the target see enemies 
around every corner, even making it look like perfectly friendly people are 
posing a threat.  It requires a holy amulet dedicated to your god to perform.
.EP
